### 手动采集：将 sourceId 改为现有且已启用的 RSS/Atom 来源
POST http://127.0.0.1:8080/api/v1/sources/1/crawl
Accept: application/json
X-Correlation-Id: idea-stage5-crawl

### 来源连通性与 Feed 解析测试（不保存文章）
POST http://127.0.0.1:8080/api/v1/sources/1/test
Accept: application/json
X-Correlation-Id: idea-stage5-source-test

### 任务分页
GET http://127.0.0.1:8080/api/v1/tasks?page=0&size=20
Accept: application/json

### 任务详情
GET http://127.0.0.1:8080/api/v1/tasks/1
Accept: application/json

### 任务明细
GET http://127.0.0.1:8080/api/v1/tasks/1/items
Accept: application/json

### 不存在的任务
GET http://127.0.0.1:8080/api/v1/tasks/999999
Accept: application/json
